    <detaileddescription>
<para>Non blocking communication predicate The message in <emphasis>Data</emphasis>, with tag <emphasis>Tag</emphasis>, is sent whenever possible to the processor with rank <emphasis>Dest</emphasis> An <emphasis>Handle</emphasis> to the message is returned to be used to check for the status of the message, using the <computeroutput>mpi_wait</computeroutput> or <computeroutput>mpi_test</computeroutput> predicates Until <computeroutput>mpi_wait</computeroutput> is called, the memory allocated for the buffer containing the message is not released </para>
